\pard\pardeftab720\sa398\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs48 \cf2 \cb3 Step 3: Create the theme.json configuration file\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa320\partightenfactor0

\f4\b0\fs25\fsmilli12800 \cf2 \cb6 Theme.json
\f1\fs32 \cb3  is a configuration file for enabling and disabling block settings and for applying styles to blocks. I will describe how to use 
\f4\fs25\fsmilli12800 \cb6 theme.json
\f1\fs32 \cb3  in detail in {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://fullsiteediting.com/lessons/global-styles/"}}{\fldrslt \cb3 \ul upcoming lessons}}, so do not worry if you are not familiar with this format yet.\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa320\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \cb3 In this lesson, you will add the layout setting: Block themes use this setting to specify the default content width and to support wide width, full width, left, center, and right alignments.\cb1 \
